The paper discusses the field of automatic text summarization, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses information retrieval (IR) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, which are relevant to sub-categories cs.IR and cs.AI, respectively. Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges and limitations of automatic summarization, which could be relevant to sub-categories cs.LG (Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
